{"tid":2204544,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人比較鍾意online上堂?","createTime":"2020-09-16T06:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T04:15:59.000Z","uid":363087,"like":267,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9d8873e69146dc174399f37836e4eb5f28e0ed","tid":2204544,"uid":363087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:34:25.000Z","msg":"1.方便<br />\n   唔使太早起身預埋搭車時間， 返8半可     以8點25分先醒<br />\n<br />\n2. 通常都有recording<br />\n   有時個lecturer上堂上得太high， 啲學生聽到一半就聽唔明， 但係佢仲一輪嘴咁講曬 啲野， 而家有recording可以停咗條片佢睇返notes 慢慢理解<br />\n<br />\n3. 時間自由同彈性好多<br />\n  以前上堂基本上你一定要喺嗰度坐定定上完堂， 依家你瞓返飽/ 打鋪機/食個早餐都仲得<br />\n<br />\n4. 有啲group project可以變單拖<br />\n唔使專登走去識人， 仲要諗佢係咪free Rider<br />\n<br />\n不過當然都有缺點，eg: 上lab要線上上會比較麻煩/ 比較難識到新friend/ 對自制能力不足嘅學生會比較易爛Grade等等<br />\n<br />\n但係就算有呢啲缺點，我都係覺得Online上堂好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3e6f9db002f28a54a9829983e14bad27b85a0e","tid":2204544,"uid":363087,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"就好似我依家明明上緊Lecture, 但仲有時間上連登開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b8ea700af24518a0002fb0cb38c3ae4cea87a8","tid":2204544,"uid":10850,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:35:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9cddd34aaa919a38673f0827c8b8aac30753ab29","tid":2204544,"uid":116466,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"7f3e6f9db002f28a54a9829983e14bad27b85a0e","tid":2204544,"uid":363087,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"就好似我依家明明上緊Lecture, 但仲有時間上連登開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:36:34.000Z","msg":"一句到尾<br />\n由課室Hea轉到屋企Hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9594151e431ec5d018382f7ae45e8b34eac2c792","tid":2204544,"uid":17124